item.title: CVE-2023-25768|2023-10-24T12:49:01.830Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20azure%20credentials%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Azure Credentials Plugin 253.v887e0f9e898b and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to connect to an attacker-specified web server.

item.title: CVE-2023-25766|2023-10-24T12:48:59.562Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20azure%20credentials%20plugin
